634
00:40:33,280 --> 00:40:34,800
I don't owe you anymore.

635
00:40:36,430 --> 00:40:37,630
Ji Bozai, actually I...

636
00:40:37,760 --> 00:40:38,760
I...

637
00:40:51,200 --> 00:40:52,200
Ming Yi,

638
00:40:53,280 --> 00:40:54,720
