never forgive them easily.

652
00:42:05,110 --> 00:42:06,110
Great.

653
00:42:06,630 --> 00:42:09,880
Situ Ling, you're quite something.

654
00:42:33,200 --> 00:42:34,200
Lord Hanfeng,

655
00:42:35,200 --> 00:42:36,200
